hm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6326,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/13\/opening-speech-of-abu-bakr-caliph\/","url_meta":{"origin":27254,"position":3},"title":"Abu Bakr on Khilafah: Inaugural address of Abu Bakr as Caliph","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Hisham reported: Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, began to speak at his inauguration, praising Allah as He deserves and saying, \u201cTo proceed: O people, I have been put in authority over you, but I am not the best of you. If I do the right thing,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6859,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/virtues-prayer-parents-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":27254,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Virtues: Prayer, goodness to parents, jihad","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: I asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which deed is best?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPrayer in its proper time.\u201d I asked, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cGood treatment of\u00a0your parents.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20098,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/daily